snippet.title: AMBER ALERT (Child Abduction Emergency) Kentucky Statewide (Suspect Armed) NOAA Weather Radio
snippet.description:
Child Abduction Emergency

KYC001-003-005-007-009-011-013-015-017-019-021-023-025-027-029- 031-033-035-037-039-041-043-045-047-049-051-053-055-057-059-061- 063-065-067-069-071-073-075-077-079-081-083-085-087-089-091-093- 095-097-099-101-103-105-107-109-111-113-115-117-119-121-123-125- 127-129-131-133-135-137-139-141-143-145-147-149-151-153-155-157- 159-161-163-165-167-169-171-173-175-177-179-181-183-185-187-189- 191-193-195-197-199-201-203-205-207-209-211-213-215-217-219-221- 223-225-227-229-231-233-235-237-239-260530- URGENT - IMMEDIATE BROADCAST REQUESTED CHILD ABDUCTION EMERGENCY KENTUCKY EMERGENCY MANAGEMENT AGENCY LOUISVILLE KENTUCKY RELAYED BY NATIONAL WEATHER SERVICE LOUISVILLE KY 1021 PM EDT WED MAR 25 2020 /921 PM CDT WED MAR 25 2020/ THE FOLLOWING MESSAGE IS TRANSMITTED AT THE REQUEST OF THE KENTUCKY EMERGENCY MANAGEMENT AGENCY LOUISVILLE KENTUCKY. AT THE REQUEST OF THE KENTUCKY STATE POLICE...THE KENTUCKY EMERGENCY ALERT SYSTEM IS ACTIVATED TO ASSIST IN THE BROADCAST OF AN AMBER ALERT. AN AMBER ALERT HAS BEEN DECLARED...REPEATING...AN AMBER ALERT HAS BEEN DECLARED. INCIDENT SUMMARY: SUSAN BLANCHARD IS THE GRANDMOTHER AND LEGAL GUARDIAN OF TWO SEVEN YEAR OLD TWINS, ISABELLA AND AUDRIANA BLANCHARD. NEELY BLANCHARD CAME TO VISIT THE TWINS ON FRIDAY MARCH 20 2020. NEELY TOOK THE TWINS TO A FRIENDS RESIDENCE IN DAWSON SPRINGS KENTUCKY. ACCORDING TO THE FRIEND THAT RESIDES IN DAWSON SPRINGS, NEELY HASN`T BEEN SEEN OR HEARD FROM SINCE MONDAY MARCH 23 2020. SUSAN BELIEVES NEELY BLANCHARD MAY BE EN ROUTE TO SOUTH CAROLINA WHERE HER 11 YEAR OLD DAUGHTER RESIDES WITH HER GRANDMOTHER. NEELY HAS A HISTORY OF MENTAL ILLNESS FURTHER COMPOUNDED BY THE CORONAVIRUS PANDEMIC. SHE IS IN POSSESSION OF A HANDGUN. SHE IS DRIVING A BLACK 2014 FORD ESCAPE WITH FLORIDA LICENCE PLATE E C L A U S E VICTIMS: ISABELLA BLANCHARD. A WHITE FEMALE AGED 7 YEARS OLD. SHE HAS GREEN EYES AND BROWN HAIR AND IS THREE FEET EIGHT INCHES TALL WEIGHING 60 POUNDS. AUDRIANNA BLANCHARD. A WHITE FEMALE AGED 7 YEARS OLD. SHE HAS GREEN EYES AND BROWN HAIR AND IS FOUR FEET TALL WEIGHING 75 POUNDS. SUSPECT: NEELY BLANCHARD. A WHITE FEMALE AGED 33 YEARS OLD. SHE HAS HAZEL EYES AND BROWN HAIR AND IS FIVE FEET EIGHT INCHES TALL WEIGHING 140 POUNDS. VEHICLE: A BLACK 2014 FORD ESCAPE WITH FLORIDA LICENCE PLATE READING E C L A U S E IF YOU HAVE ANY INFORMATION REGARDING THIS ALERT PLEASE CONTACT THE KENTUCKY STATE POLICE. 

$$
 BJS
